Blaze Security
==========
Blaze Security is a framework for arbitrary security models.

What is it?
===========

Blaze Security is a framework for Java SE 6 and EE 6 environments,
that can be used to enforce any security model. It supports fine
grained security features like field access checks and object
based permissions.


How to use it?
==============
Include the jars you want in your project and get started!

Contents of distribution
========================

api, impl
 
